{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775866093568,"sessionID":"ses_28622b5aaffeoroE3FWnTlVsJJ","part":{"id":"prt_d79de15c2001j29WluGsE1lvpL","messageID":"msg_d79dd9ca40019rcyAvpb0ls0xi","sessionID":"ses_28622b5aaffeoroE3FWnTlVsJJ","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-012/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-012/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-012 Tasks: 会话存储接口定义 (Session Store Interface Definition)\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: - **AR:** AR-012\n5: - **Module:** pkg/store\n6: - **Language:** Go\n7: - **Size:** S\n8: - **Status:** Stage ST-3 (Design) Completed\n9: \n10: ## Task Checklist\n11: \n12: ### T1: Core Store Interface [COMPLETED]\n13: - [x] Define `Store` interface with all required methods\n14: - [x] Define `ErrNotFound` error variable\n15: - [x] Document interface methods with proper GoDoc comments\n16: - **Verification:** Interface compiles and methods match delta-spec requirements\n17: - **Files:** `pkg/store/store.go`\n18: \n19: ### T2: Redis Store Implementation\n20: - [ ] Create `store_redis.go` with Redis client struct\n21: - [ ] Implement `Ping()` - verify connectivity with PING/PONG\n22: - [ ] Implement `GetSandboxBySessionID()` - GET session:{id} with ErrNotFound handling\n23: - [ ] Implement `StoreSandbox()` - SETNX + ZADD expiry + ZADD activity in pipeline\n24: - [ ] Implement `UpdateSandbox()` - SET with XX flag\n25: - [ ] Implement `DeleteSandboxBySessionID()` - DEL + ZREM expiry + ZREM activity in pipeline\n26: - [ ] Implement `ListExpiredSandboxes()` - ZRANGEBYSCORE session:expiry\n27: - [ ] Implement `ListInactiveSandboxes()` - ZRANGEBYSCORE session:last_activity\n28: - [ ] Implement `UpdateSessionLastActivity()` - ZADD with existence check\n29: - [ ] Implement `Close()` - close Redis client connection\n30: - **Verification:** All methods pass unit tests against Redis test server\n31: - **Files:** `pkg/store/store_redis.go`\n32: \n33: ### T3: Valkey Store Implementation\n34: - [ ] Create `store_valkey.go` with Valkey client struct\n35: - [ ] Implement `Ping()` - verify connectivity\n36: - [ ] Implement `GetSandboxBySessionID()` - GET with IsValkeyNil handling\n37: - [ ] Implement `StoreSandbox()` - atomic pipeline operations\n38: - [ ] Implement `UpdateSandbox()` - update with existence check\n39: - [ ] Implement `DeleteSandboxBySessionID()` - cleanup with pipeline\n40: - [ ] Implement `ListExpiredSandboxes()` - ZRANGEBYSCORE with MGET\n41: - [ ] Implement `ListInactiveSandboxes()` - ZRANGEBYSCORE with MGET\n42: - [ ] Implement `UpdateSessionLastActivity()` - ZADD with validation\n43: - [ ] Implement `Close()` - close Valkey client connection\n44: - **Verification:** All methods pass unit tests against Valkey test server\n45: - **Files:** `pkg/store/store_valkey.go`\n46: \n47: ### T4: Singleton Access Pattern\n48: - [ ] Create `singleton.go` with `Storage()` function\n49: - [ ] Implement `sync.Once` for thread-safe initialization\n50: - [ ] Implement provider selection via `STORE_TYPE` env var\n51: - [ ] Implement Redis configuration parsing (`REDIS_ADDR`, `REDIS_PASSWORD`, `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED`)\n52: - [ ] Implement Valkey configuration parsing (`VALKEY_ADDR`, `VALKEY_PASSWORD`, `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE`, `VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE`)\n53: - [ ] Add `klog.Fatalf` on initialization failure\n54: - **Verification:** Concurrent calls return same instance; invalid config logs fatal\n55: - **Files:** `pkg/store/singleton.go`\n56: \n57: ### T5: Error Definitions & Constants\n58: - [ ] Define store constants (`sessionPrefix`, `expiryIndexKey`, `lastActivityIndexKey`)\n59: - [ ] Define provider type constants (`redisStoreType`, `valkeyStoreType`)\n60: - [ ] Ensure `ErrNotFound` is exported and properly documented\n61: - **Verification:** Constants match delta-spec values exactly\n62: - **Files:** `pkg/store/store.go`, `pkg/store/singleton.go`\n63: \n64: ### T6: Unit Tests - Store Interface\n65: - [ ] Write interface contract tests (nil handling, empty strings)\n66: - [ ] Test `ErrNotFound` is returned correctly\n67: - **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/store/... -run TestInterface` passes\n68: - **Files:** `pkg/store/store_test.go`\n69: \n70: ### T7: Unit Tests - Redis Implementation\n71: - [ ] Test `Ping()` success and failure scenarios\n72: - [ ] Test `GetSandboxBySessionID()` with missing key returns `ErrNotFound`\n73: - [ ] Test `StoreSandbox()` validation (nil, zero ExpiresAt, empty SessionID)\n74: - [ ] Test `StoreSandbox()` atomic pipeline execution\n75: - [ ] Test `UpdateSandbox()` XX flag behavior\n76: - [ ] Test `DeleteSandboxBySessionID()` cleanup of all keys\n77: - [ ] Test `ListExpiredSandboxes()` with limit=0 returns empty\n78: - [ ] Test `ListInactiveSandboxes()` orphan tolerance\n79: - [ ] Test `UpdateSessionLastActivity()` zero time defaults to now\n80: - [ ] Test `Close()` releases connection\n81: - **Verification:** Tests pass with `go test ./pkg/store/... -run TestRedis`\n82: - **Files:** `pkg/store/store_redis_test.go`\n83: \n84: ### T8: Unit Tests - Valkey Implementation\n85: - [ ] Test all scenarios from T7 for Valkey backend\n86: - [ ] Test `IsValkeyNil` error translation to `ErrNotFound`\n87: - [ ] Test comma-separated address parsing\n88: - [ ] Test `DisableCache` and `ForceSingleClient` options\n89: - **Verification:** Tests pass with `go test ./pkg/store/... -run TestValkey`\n90: - **Files:** `pkg/store/store_valkey_test.go`\n91: \n92: ### T9: Unit Tests - Singleton Pattern\n93: - [ ] Test concurrent access returns same instance\n94: - [ ] Test `STORE_TYPE` case-insensitive parsing\n95: - [ ] Test default to Redis when `STORE_TYPE` unset\n96: - [ ] Test invalid `STORE_TYPE` fails initialization\n97: - [ ] Test Redis environment validation (required vars)\n98: - [ ] Test Valkey environment validation (required vars)\n99: - **Verification:** Tests pass with `go test ./pkg/store/... -run TestSingleton`\n100: - **Files:** `pkg/store/singleton_test.go`\n101: \n102: ### T10: Dependencies & Build\n103: - [ ] Add `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` to go.mod\n104: - [ ] Add `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` to go.mod\n105: - [ ] Run `go mod tidy` to update dependencies\n106: - [ ] Verify build succeeds: `go build ./pkg/store/...`\n107: - **Verification:** No build errors; imports resolve correctly\n108: - **Files:** `go.mod`, `go.sum`\n109: \n110: ### T11: Documentation\n111: - [ ] Add package-level GoDoc for `pkg/store`\n112: - [ ] Document environment variable configuration\n113: - [ ] Add usage examples in code comments\n114: - [ ] Update changes/AR-012/design.md with implementation details\n115: - **Verification:** `go doc ./pkg/store` displays properly\n116: - **Files:** `pkg/store/doc.go` (optional), code comments\n117: \n118: ## Verification Commands\n119: \n120: ```bash\n121: # Build verification\n122: go build ./pkg/store/...\n123: \n124: # Test verification\n125: go test ./pkg/store/... -v\n126: \n127: # Race detection\n128: go test ./pkg/store/... -race\n129: \n130: # Coverage report\n131: go test ./pkg/store/... -cover\n132: ```\n133: \n134: ## Dependencies\n135: \n136: - AR-010: Router 会话管理 (Session Management)\n137: - `pkg/common/types` for `SandboxInfo` type\n138: \n139: ## Notes\n140: \n141: - Store interface already defined in `pkg/store/store.go` (completed prior)\n142: - Use testcontainers or embedded Redis/Valkey for integration tests\n143: - All store operations must be atomic (use pipelines/multi)\n144: - Orphan tolerance: list operations skip missing keys without failing\n\n(End of file - total 144 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-012 Tasks: 会话存储接口定义 (Session Store Interface Definition)\n\n## Overview\n- **AR:** AR-012\n- **Module:** pkg/store\n- **Language:** Go\n- **Size:** S\n- **Status:** Stage S