{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775866198580,"sessionID":"ses_28622b5aaffeoroE3FWnTlVsJJ","part":{"id":"prt_d79dec79f001vC9DG3wjLSvh4Z","messageID":"msg_d79de6e9e001wdLcxa3mk42WUI","sessionID":"ses_28622b5aaffeoroE3FWnTlVsJJ","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:13","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-013/design.md","content":"# AR-013 Design Document\n\n## Redis 存储实现\n\n## Overview\n\n(TBD - Design to be completed)\n\n## Redis Client Architecture\n\n(TBD)\n\n## Store Method Implementations\n\n(TBD)\n\n## Index Management Strategy\n\n(TBD)\n\n## Error Handling\n\n(TBD)\n\n## Pipeline Operations\n\n(TBD)\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n(TBD)\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-012/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-013/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-013/design.md","time":{"start":1775866198554,"end":1775866198579}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775866198582,"sessionID":"ses_28622b5aaffeoroE3FWnTlVsJJ","part":{"id":"prt_d79ded805001C0N637LFbH9y9G","messageID":"msg_d79de6e9e001wdLcxa3mk42WUI","sessionID":"ses_28622b5aaffeoroE3FWnTlVsJJ","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:14","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-013/delta-spec.md","content":"# AR-013: Redis 存储实现 (Redis Storage Implementation) - Delta Specification\n\n## Overview\n\n**AR ID:** AR-013  \n**Module:** `pkg/store`  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** M  \n**Base Spec:** [AR-012: 会话存储接口定义](../AR-012/delta-spec.md)\n\nThe Redis Storage Implementation provides a concrete implementation of the Store interface using Redis as the backend. It handles connection management, command execution, and Redis-specific error handling while maintaining compatibility with the abstract Store interface defined in AR-012.\n\n---\n\n## Requirements\n\n(TBD - Requirements to be defined based on AR-012 interface contract)\n\n---\n\n## Changes to Base Specification\n\nNo modifications to existing interfaces. This AR implements the Store interface defined in AR-012 for Redis backend.\n\n---\n\n## New Interfaces\n\n(TBD - Implementation-specific types and functions)\n\n---\n\n## Modified Interfaces\n\nNone. This AR implements existing interfaces without modification.\n\n---\n\n## Behavioral Changes\n\n| Behavior | Before | After |\n|----------|--------|-------|\n| Redis Store | Interface only | Full Redis implementation |\n| Connection management | None | Redis client with pooling |\n| Command execution | None | Full Redis command support |\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Version | Purpose |\n|------------|---------|---------|\n| `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` | v9.x | Redis client for Go |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store` | Local | Store interface definition |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types` | Local | SandboxInfo type definition |\n\n---\n\n## File Index\n\n| Path | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `pkg/store/store_redis.go` | Redis Store implementation |\n\n---\n\n## Constants\n\n(TBD)\n\n---\n\n## Environment Variables\n\n(TBD - Redis-specific configuration)\n\n---\n\n## API Endpoints Summary\n\nThis AR provides library functionality; no HTTP endpoints are directly exposed.\n\n---\n\n## Migration Notes\n\n- **New dependencies**: Add `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` to go.mod\n- **Environment setup**: Configure `REDIS_ADDR` and `REDIS_PASSWORD`\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria Summary\n\n1. **Implementation Completeness**: All Store interface methods implemented\n2. **Error Handling**: Redis errors properly translated to store errors\n3. **Atomicity**: Pipeline operations ensure atomic writes\n4. **Index Management**: ZSET indexes maintained correctly\n5. **Connection Management**: Proper client lifecycle handling\n6. **Test Coverage**: Unit and integration tests pass\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-012/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-013/delta-spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-013/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775866198557,"end":1775866198581}}}}
