{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775866198585,"sessionID":"ses_28622b5aaffeoroE3FWnTlVsJJ","part":{"id":"prt_d79df2dc70017LrqkDkVLwIpEb","messageID":"msg_d79de6e9e001wdLcxa3mk42WUI","sessionID":"ses_28622b5aaffeoroE3FWnTlVsJJ","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:16","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-013/tasks.md","content":"# AR-013 Tasks: Redis 存储实现 (Redis Storage Implementation)\n\n## Overview\n- **AR:** AR-013\n- **Module:** pkg/store\n- **Language:** Go\n- **Size:** M\n- **Status:** Stage ST-1 (Open)\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### T1: Redis Client Setup [PENDING]\n- [ ] Create `store_redis.go` with RedisStore struct\n- [ ] Define Redis client configuration structure\n- [ ] Implement Redis client initialization with connection pooling\n- [ ] Implement connection validation (Ping/PONG)\n- **Verification:** Client connects to Redis server successfully\n- **Files:** `pkg/store/store_redis.go`\n\n### T2: Core Store Methods - Read Operations [PENDING]\n- [ ] Implement `Ping()` - verify connectivity with PING/PONG\n- [ ] Implement `GetSandboxBySessionID()` - GET session:{id}\n- [ ] Handle `redis.Nil` error and translate to `ErrNotFound`\n- [ ] Implement `ListExpiredSandboxes()` - ZRANGEBYSCORE + MGET\n- [ ] Implement `ListInactiveSandboxes()` - ZRANGEBYSCORE + MGET\n- [ ] Handle orphaned ZSET entries gracefully\n- **Verification:** All read operations return correct data or errors\n- **Files:** `pkg/store/store_redis.go`\n\n### T3: Core Store Methods - Write Operations [PENDING]\n- [ ] Implement `StoreSandbox()` - SETNX + ZADD (atomic pipeline)\n- [ ] Validate sandbox and ExpiresAt before write\n- [ ] Implement `UpdateSandbox()` - SET with XX flag\n- [ ] Implement `UpdateSessionLastActivity()` - ZADD with existence check\n- [ ] Implement `DeleteSandboxBySessionID()` - DEL + ZREM (atomic pipeline)\n- [ ] Ensure atomicity using Redis pipeline/multi\n- **Verification:** All write operations are atomic and consistent\n- **Files:** `pkg/store/store_redis.go`\n\n### T4: Connection Management [PENDING]\n- [ ] Implement `Close()` - close Redis client connection\n- [ ] Handle connection pool cleanup\n- [ ] Implement proper resource disposal\n- **Verification:** Close releases all connections without leaks\n- **Files:** `pkg/store/store_redis.go`\n\n### T5: Error Handling [PENDING]\n- [ ] Define Redis-specific error types\n- [ ] Implement `redis.Nil` → `ErrNotFound` translation\n- [ ] Handle connection errors appropriately\n- [ ] Add context timeout handling\n- **Verification:** All Redis errors are properly handled and translated\n- **Files:** `pkg/store/store_redis.go`\n\n### T6: Unit Tests - Mock Redis [PENDING]\n- [ ] Set up mock Redis client for testing\n- [ ] Test `Ping()` success and failure\n- [ ] Test `GetSandboxBySessionID()` - found and not found cases\n- [ ] Test `StoreSandbox()` validation and success\n- [ ] Test `UpdateSandbox()` - exists and not exists\n- [ ] Test `DeleteSandboxBySessionID()` cleanup\n- [ ] Test `ListExpiredSandboxes()` with various limits\n- [ ] Test `ListInactiveSandboxes()` orphan tolerance\n- [ ] Test `UpdateSessionLastActivity()` with zero time\n- [ ] Test `Close()` behavior\n- **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/store/... -run TestRedis` passes\n- **Files:** `pkg/store/store_redis_test.go`\n\n### T7: Integration Tests [PENDING]\n- [ ] Set up Redis test container or embedded server\n- [ ] Test full CRUD operations against real Redis\n- [ ] Test concurrent access scenarios\n- [ ] Test pipeline atomicity under failure conditions\n- [ ] Test index consistency after operations\n- **Verification:** Integration tests pass with real Redis\n- **Files:** `pkg/store/store_redis_integration_test.go`\n\n### T8: Dependencies & Build [PENDING]\n- [ ] Ensure `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` is in go.mod\n- [ ] Run `go mod tidy` to update dependencies\n- [ ] Verify build succeeds: `go build ./pkg/store/...`\n- **Verification:** No build errors; imports resolve correctly\n- **Files:** `go.mod`, `go.sum`\n\n### T9: Documentation [PENDING]\n- [ ] Add GoDoc comments for RedisStore type\n- [ ] Document Redis-specific configuration options\n- [ ] Add usage examples in code comments\n- [ ] Update changes/AR-013/design.md with implementation details\n- **Verification:** `go doc ./pkg/store` displays Redis implementation\n- **Files:** `pkg/store/store_redis.go`\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n```bash\n# Build verification\ngo build ./pkg/store/...\n\n# Unit test verification\ngo test ./pkg/store/... -v -run TestRedis\n\n# Integration test verification\ngo test ./pkg/store/... -v -run Integration\n\n# Race detection\ngo test ./pkg/store/... -race\n\n# Coverage report\ngo test ./pkg/store/... -cover\n```\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- AR-012: 会话存储接口定义 (Store Interface must be defined)\n- `pkg/common/types` for `SandboxInfo` type\n- `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` for Redis client\n\n## Notes\n\n- Follow the interface contract defined in AR-012 exactly\n- Use Redis pipeline for atomic multi-command operations\n- Always translate `redis.Nil` to `store.ErrNotFound`\n- Handle orphaned ZSET entries in list operations\n- Ensure proper connection cleanup in Close()\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-012/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-013/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-013/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775866198563,"end":1775866198584}}}}
