{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775866198951,"sessionID":"ses_28622b5aaffeoroE3FWnTlVsJJ","part":{"id":"prt_d79de8082001rvbPwGtjoSpse1","messageID":"msg_d79de6e9e001wdLcxa3mk42WUI","sessionID":"ses_28622b5aaffeoroE3FWnTlVsJJ","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:11","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-013/spec.yaml","content":"id: AR-013\ntitle: Redis 存储实现\nmodule: pkg/store\nlanguage: Go\nsize: M\nstatus: open\n\n# AR-013: Redis 存储实现\n# Module: pkg/store\n# Language: Go\n# Size: M\n\n# OpenSpec Metadata\nopenspec:\n  version: \"1.0\"\n  project: agentcube\n\n# Architecture Requirement\nrequirement:\n  type: redis-storage-implementation\n  description: |\n    Implement the Redis storage backend for the session store interface.\n    This provides a concrete implementation of the Store interface using\n    Redis as the underlying storage engine, supporting session persistence,\n    expiry tracking, and activity indexing.\n\n# Scope\nscope:\n  in:\n    - Redis Store implementation of Store interface\n    - Redis client configuration and connection management\n    - CRUD operations for session data using Redis commands\n    - Expiry and activity index management with Redis ZSET\n    - Error handling and Redis-specific error translation\n    - Pipeline/Multi operations for atomicity\n  out:\n    - Valkey implementation (covered in separate AR)\n    - Migration logic from other storage backends\n    - Caching layer optimizations\n    - Redis Cluster-specific features\n\n# Acceptance Criteria\nacceptance:\n  - All Store interface methods implemented for Redis backend\n  - Redis connection pooling and lifecycle management\n  - Proper error translation (redis.Nil → ErrNotFound)\n  - Atomic pipeline operations for StoreSandbox and DeleteSandboxBySessionID\n  - ZSET index management for expiry and activity tracking\n  - Environment variable configuration support\n  - Unit tests with mocked Redis client\n  - Integration tests with Redis test server\n\n# References\nreferences:\n  - AR-012: 会话存储接口定义\n\n# Estimation\nestimation:\n  size: M\n  story_points: 5\n  days: 3\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-012/spec.yaml":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-013/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-013/spec.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-013/spec.yaml","time":{"start":1775866198546,"end":1775866198948}}}}
